Oh boy.

00:17:05.890 --> 00:17:06.390
A wolf.

00:17:10.778 --> 00:17:11.319
AUDIENCE: Hi.

00:17:11.319 --> 00:17:13.920
Is there a technical
term for the hair piece

00:17:13.920 --> 00:17:15.150
that your character wears?

