AUDIENCE: I was
wondering if-- I find

00:23:41.110 --> 00:23:44.210
that I have certain
typographical mistakes that I

00:23:44.210 --> 00:23:48.770
make, especially when I'm
typing quickly, that bother me.

00:23:48.770 --> 00:23:52.270
And I was wondering
whether a lot was a thing

00:23:52.270 --> 00:23:54.230
that you use to help
correct yourself,

00:23:54.230 --> 00:23:57.580
or whether there are other
mistakes like that you're

00:23:57.580 --> 00:23:59.210
trying to fight?

