00:24:07.840 --> 00:24:10.130
except for if there's a
double letter in there.

00:24:10.130 --> 00:24:12.480
If there's two L's or
two T's, I'm fucked.

00:24:12.480 --> 00:24:15.160
I don't know how
to spell the word.

00:24:15.160 --> 00:24:16.877
So I've been trying
to memorize which

00:24:16.877 --> 00:24:18.085
ones have the double letters.

00:24:22.544 --> 00:24:24.585
AUDIENCE: So, he beat me
to it, but the Alot post

00:24:24.585 --> 00:24:25.440
